NEW
100 REM *** HYBRID SCROLL RUNNER ***
110 GOSUB 9000
120 REM MAIN LOOP
130 GOSUB 5000
140 POKE 252,PLAYERX
150 SYS 49664
160 IF PEEK(253)=0 THEN PLAYERX=PEEK(252)
